# ILOs for this week

- Critically evaluate the literature on changes in mental health at menopause
- Discuss possible causes for changes in mental health at menopause, including changes in hormone levels/receptivity, physical symptoms of menopause, and sociocultural factors
- Discuss treatments to alleviate menopausal symptoms, and the possible impacts of these treatments on mental health

